rows.label: campfev11_420_100_msg0004
rows.name:
But truth be told, you're
struggling with that monster on
the Orlato Mountain Pass, right?

rows.label: campfev11_420_100_msg0006
rows.name: I-it's fine... We'll win next time.

rows.label: campfev11_420_100_msg0007
rows.name: Well, I'll try to do my best, too.

rows.label: campfev11_420_100_msg0008
rows.name:
It's not a good look to be
struggling like this when I'm
supposed to be the one helping.
